OL,4,CMarble Arch Mound: Deputy leader
OL,5,Cresigns amid spiralling costs
OL,6, The deputy leader of a London council
OL,7, responsible for the ballooning costs of
OL,8, the Marble Arch Mound has resigned.
OL,10,FMelvyn Caplan stepped down immediately
OL,11,Fafter total costs nearly doubled to
OL,12,F#6m, up from a forecast of #3.3m.
OL,14,FTicketholders were offered refunds for
OL,15,Fthe artificial viewing platform which
OL,16,Ftemporarily closed within two days of
OL,17,Fopening on 26 July.
OL,19,FA review to "understand what went wrong
OL,20,Fand ensure it never happens again" is
OL,21,Funder way, Westminster Council said.
